text: KFWG-LP (98.3 FM) is a low-power FM radio station licensed to Clinton, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Universal Truth Radio, LTD ==History== The station call sign KFWG-LP on February 25, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * * Oklahoma Catholic Broadcasting Network FWG-LP FWG-LP Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in Oklahoma FWG-LP
